			<h4><a id="comment_link_71937" name="comment_link_71937" href="//use.perl.org/comments.pl?sid=44783&amp;cid=71937" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(71937)">Off-topic (Perl 6 syntax)</a>
			
			<span id="comment_score_71937" class="score">(<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 71937); return false">Score:1</a>)</span></h4>
		</div>
